{"tid":1473254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尊重對家立場","createTime":"2019-08-14T19:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T19:41:26.000Z","uid":176905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dd55fd794ee4fa969cee383ea23a28b992a5ccbe","tid":1473254,"uid":176905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:39:55.000Z","msg":"你想拎咩色身份證呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470191</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n相信大家已經睇過藍/黃色身分證呢個故仔<br />\n<br />\n其實香港真係有班人係會簡藍色身分證，當大家遇到呢啲人既時候麻煩唔好屌鳩佢地，因為佢地係有權選擇自己既立場去支持送中。<br />\n<br />\n但面對住3毛5毛或者又要鬧示威者又唔敢揀藍色身分證嗰種人，麻煩大家大大力咁去屌爛佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a64b9b72b7b8fb6f5bc758f612e99e0c90a71371","tid":1473254,"uid":178013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:41:26.000Z","msg":"【8.18】 屌! 又話要贏? 又話要除低口罩相見?  團結呀香港人!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEKtPS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dEKtPS</a>"}]}